channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Notre Dame Unveils Shamrock Series Uniforms For Game Against Army At Yankee Stadium
item.description: Notre Dame unveiled its latest Shamrock Series uniforms, which are inspired by the "Four Horsemen" and will be worn against Army at Yankee Stadium on Nov. 23.

item.title: Are The Kansas City Chiefs Considering Alternate Uniforms?
item.description: Don't expect the Kansas City Chiefs to get an alternate uniform anytime soon, though their owner appears to be warming up to the idea.
